			DORAND 3
				SAY Please, call us servers.
				SAY I am here to serve thee as best I can, <SRC.SEX milord/milady>.
				SAY If I can help thee, I certainly shall, <SRC.SEX milord/milady>.
			ENDDO
		ELSE
			DORAND 3
				SAY Please, call us servers.
